item.description:
This tour will introduce you to all the new major visual features in Xfce 4.8. This is only the visual part of what has been done; for a full list of changes, see the Xfce 4.8 changelog .
File Manager (thunar) Remote shares browsing Thunar now has optional support for GVFS which will allow you to browse remote shares using Thunar: FTP, Windows Shares, WebDav and SSH servers&hellip;
Thunar browsing a remote share New file operations progress dialog When several file operations (copy or move) are being handled in parallel, Thunar now shows a single progress dialog which displays all the relevant information.
